casebody.data:
Columbus Bar Association v. Ryan.

[Cite as Columbus Bar Assn. v. Ryan (1989), 45 Ohio St. 3d 374.]

(No. 89-719 Submitted July 11, 1989 Decided October 4, 1989.) *375Ransier & Ransier, Frederick Ransier III, Bruce Campbell, Cotruvo & Cusack and Mary Jo Cusack, for relator. Frank A. Ray, for respondent. Per Curiam.

Having thoroughly reviewed the record, we concur in the board’s findings and recommendation. Respondent is hereby suspended indefinitely from the practice of law in Ohio. Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
